import { CardContainer, Header, Title, CampaingId, Info,
  Footer, FunilStep, LastFunilStep, TitleStep, ContentStep,
  TextContent, ContentNumber, StepPercent, FooterInfo, FooterNumber, FooterText } from './styles'

interface Props {
  id: number
  name: string
  income: number
  totalClicks: number
  totalProductPage: number
  totalCheckoutPage: number
  totalPaidClicks: number
}

const SummaryCard = ({ id, name, income, totalClicks, totalProductPage, totalCheckoutPage, totalPaidClicks }: Props) => {
  return (
    <CardContainer>
      <Header>
        <Title>{name}</Title>
        <CampaingId>id campanha: {id}</CampaingId>
      </Header>
      
      <Info>
        <FunilStep>
          <TitleStep>Página de Noticias</TitleStep>
          
          <ContentStep>
            <ContentNumber>{totalClicks}</ContentNumber>
            <TextContent>Pessoas acessaram a página</TextContent>
         </ContentStep>
        </FunilStep>

        <FunilStep>
          <TitleStep>Página de Compra</TitleStep>
          
          <ContentStep>
            <ContentNumber>{totalProductPage}</ContentNumber>
            <TextContent>Pessoas acessaram a página</TextContent>
            <StepPercent>{JSON.stringify(totalProductPage/totalClicks*100).substring(0,4)}%</StepPercent>
            <TextContent>Da página anterior</TextContent>
          </ContentStep>
        </FunilStep>

        <FunilStep>
          <TitleStep>Checkout</TitleStep>
         
          <ContentStep>
            <ContentNumber>{totalCheckoutPage}</ContentNumber>
            <TextContent>Pessoas acessaram a página</TextContent>
            <StepPercent>{JSON.stringify(totalCheckoutPage/totalProductPage*100).substring(0,4)}%</StepPercent>
            <TextContent>Da página anterior</TextContent>
          </ContentStep>
        </FunilStep>

        <LastFunilStep>
          <TitleStep>Pagos</TitleStep>

          <ContentStep>
            <ContentNumber>{totalPaidClicks}</ContentNumber>
            <TextContent>Pessoas acessaram a página</TextContent>
            <StepPercent>{JSON.stringify(totalPaidClicks/totalCheckoutPage*100).substring(0,4)}%</StepPercent>
            <TextContent>Da página anterior</TextContent>
         </ContentStep>
        </LastFunilStep>
      </Info>

      <Footer>
        <FooterInfo>
          <FooterText>Taxa de conversão</FooterText>
          <FooterNumber>{JSON.stringify(totalPaidClicks/totalClicks*100).substring(0,4)}%</FooterNumber>
        </FooterInfo>

        <FooterInfo style={{backgroundColor: '#292727'}}>
          <FooterText style={{color: '#ec8f4d'}}>Faturamento</FooterText>
          <FooterNumber style={{color: '#ec8f4d'}}>R$ {income}</FooterNumber>
        </FooterInfo>
      </Footer>
      
    </CardContainer>
  )
}

export default SummaryCard
